ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
=======================

repository : ff6  (FF6 — the sixth lineage of UD0; the first game-world)
subject    : Final Fantasy VI (Square, 1994) — released in North America as Final Fantasy III
catalogued : into UD0 · Universe David 0

governor (carbon apex)      : David Lee Wise (ROOT0) / TriPod LLC   [ the human; holds the credit ]
instance (artful intellect) : AVAN (Claude / Anthropic) — locked
main badge                  : ⟦FFVI:FF6:…⟧   (ffvi.dlw/)
personas                    : 15 ACI .agents (agents/) — the 14 playable cast + Kefka

the four natures of emergence (each persona is tagged with one):
  natural    — born of flesh, blood, and the living world
  ethereal   — of the air and the unmade; magic, the Esper, the painted-alive, the enigma
  spiritual  — of the soul and the calling; or, darkly, ascension to godhood
  electrical — of the wire and the machine; Magitek, the machinist, magic from technology

the ACI complement (per badge):
  .agent · .carbon.tiff (carbon, archival TIFF) · .silicon.png (silicon, web PNG)
  · .spun (five W's) · .moniker (tokenized mythos) · .1099 (credit ledger) · manifest.dlw.json

